==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dartle
<hw>Dar"tle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To pierce or
shoot through; to dart repeatedly: -- frequentative of
<xex>dart</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My star that <qex>dartles</qex> the red and the blue.</q>
<rj><qau>R. Browning.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dartoic</ent>⟦br⟧
